@startuml
title JobRunr Enterprise Scheduler (Colored + Numbered Flow)

' 🎨 Colors
skinparam backgroundColor #F9FAFB
skinparam participant {
BackgroundColor #E3F2FD
BorderColor #1E88E5
}
skinparam database {
BackgroundColor #FFF3E0
BorderColor #FB8C00
}
skinparam actor {
BackgroundColor #E8F5E9
BorderColor #43A047
}

actor User

participant "1️⃣ React UI" as UI #BBDEFB
participant "2️⃣ API Service\n(Spring Boot)" as API #90CAF9
participant "3️⃣ Job Scheduler\n(JobRunr)" as JS #64B5F6
participant "4️⃣ Recurring Manager" as RJ #4FC3F7
database "5️⃣ PostgreSQL\n(Job Tables)" as DB #FFE0B2
participant "6️⃣ Worker Pod 1" as W1 #C8E6C9
participant "7️⃣ Worker Pod 2" as W2 #A5D6A7
participant "8️⃣ External Service" as EXT #D1C4E9
participant "9️⃣ Kafka / DLQ" as KAFKA #FFCDD2

== 🟢 JOB CREATION FLOW ==

User -> UI : 1. Create Job
UI -> API : 2. POST /jobs
API -> JS : 3. enqueue(job)
JS -> DB : 4. INSERT (ENQUEUED)
DB --> JS : 5. OK
JS --> API : 6. jobId
API --> UI : 7. Success

== 🔵 RECURRING JOB FLOW ==

RJ -> DB : 8. Scan recurring jobs
RJ -> DB : 9. Create job instance

== 🟡 DISTRIBUTED POLLING ==

loop Poll every few seconds
W1 -> DB : 10. SELECT FOR UPDATE SKIP LOCKED
DB --> W1 : 11. Job A

W2 -> DB : 12. SELECT FOR UPDATE SKIP LOCKED
DB --> W2 : 13. Job B

end

== 🟣 EXECUTION FLOW ==

W1 -> DB : 14. Mark PROCESSING
W1 -> EXT : 15. Execute Job

alt ✅ Success
EXT --> W1 : 16. Response OK
W1 -> DB : 17. Mark SUCCEEDED
else ❌ Failure
EXT --> W1 : 18. Error
W1 -> DB : 19. Mark FAILED + retry++

alt 🔁 Retry Available
    W1 -> DB : 20. Re-enqueue (delayed)
else 💀 Max Retry Exceeded
    W1 -> DB : 21. Mark DEAD
    W1 -> KAFKA : 22. Send to DLQ
end

end

== 🟠 HEARTBEAT ==

loop every 15s
W1 -> DB : 23. Heartbeat
W2 -> DB : 24. Heartbeat
end

== 🔴 FAILURE RECOVERY ==

note over DB
25. Worker crash scenario:

- लॉक released automatically
- Job becomes visible again
- Picked by another worker
  end note

@enduml
